:: Examples of open source {"position":"350,600","size":"100,100"}
Linux
- A free open sourc eoperationg system that use used on many things from personal computers to servers and is know for having many variations for many use cases.

Git
- Free open source that allows you to share repositiories and allows many people to make work on projects at the same time from different computers.

VS Code
-Its a free open source code editor that supports many laungaages and extentions to add in new features.

Audacity
-Its a free open source audio editing program that allows users to record edit and mix sounds easier

Android
-Android at its core is a open source oporation used for mobile divices like phones and tablets. It is developed by good and allows developers to make custom experiences for their phones



